      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. Honestly, it's like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014flawless inside and out! I've babied this car since day one, and it still has that brand-new feel and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s essentially perfect without the dealership price tag, you\u2019ve found it! Swing by and take a look, you're going to love it!",
      "price": 43900.0,
