      "description": "Offered is a concours-level 2004 BMW M3 (E46), a definitive analog masterpiece. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure dual-VANOS system for razor-sharp throttle response. Power is channeled through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis is structurally sound with documented subframe reinforcement, while the suspension maintains factory-spec kinematics for a pure, unadulterated driving experience. Meticulously maintained with no mechanical compromise, this is a collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
